trans-unit.source: Provides a description of modifications done to entities by operations returned in a <xref href="System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en beskrivelse av endringer utføres enheter av operasjoner som er returnert i en <xref href="System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.SaveChanges%2A> method returns a <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse> object that contains a series of <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.OperationResponse> objects, each of which contains a sequence of <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.EntityDescriptor> or LinkDescriptor instances that represent persisted changes.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.SaveChanges%2A>metoden returnerer en <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse>objekt som inneholder en rekke <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.OperationResponse>objekter, som inneholder en sekvens med <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.EntityDescriptor>eller LinkDescriptor forekomstene som representerer faste endringer.</xref:System.Data.Services.Client.EntityDescriptor> </xref:System.Data.Services.Client.OperationResponse> </xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse> </xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.SaveChanges%2A>

trans-unit.source: For successful operations, the <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.EntityDescriptor.State%2A> property of the descriptor is set to unchanged and the new values for insert and update operations are merged according to the merge settings.
trans-unit.target: For at operasjoner i <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.EntityDescriptor.State%2A>for beskrivelsen er satt til uendret, og de nye verdiene for insert og update-operasjoner er slått sammen i samsvar med innstillingene for sammenslåing.</xref:System.Data.Services.Client.EntityDescriptor.State%2A>

trans-unit.source: For operations with errors, the <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.EntityDescriptor.State%2A> of the descriptor will remain the same as they were before <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.SaveChanges%2A> was called.
trans-unit.target: For operasjoner med feil, den <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.EntityDescriptor.State%2A>på beskrivelsen forblir det samme som de var før <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.SaveChanges%2A>ble kalt.</xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.SaveChanges%2A> </xref:System.Data.Services.Client.EntityDescriptor.State%2A>

trans-unit.source: If an error occurred and processing stopped during an operation, the <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.EntityDescriptor.State%2A> will remain unchanged.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det oppstod en feilen og behandlingen stoppet under en operasjon i <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.EntityDescriptor.State%2A>forblir uendret.</xref:System.Data.Services.Client.EntityDescriptor.State%2A>

trans-unit.target: En kildeenheten i en kobling som returneres av en <xref href="System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse"> </xref>.

trans-unit.target: ID-egenskapen for kildeenheten i en kobling som returneres av en <xref href="System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse"> </xref>.

trans-unit.target: Streng-identifikator for en ID-egenskap i en kildeenheten.

trans-unit.target: Kildeenheten i en kobling som returneres av en <xref href="System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse"> </xref>.
